Program: The Forum
Title: Invisibility
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p021syl1
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 7 Jul 2014
Would you like to become invisible? What does invisibility mean anyway: is it just a matter of advanced optics, or something deeper that pre-dates science? Samira Ahmed discusses these issues with science writer Philip Ball, philosopher Kenan Malik, and psychologist Susan Blackmore. Photo by Shan Pillay (BBC) Show less